<br>
Posting applications here will not get you officers support.<br>
<br>
Any new applicant needs to.<br>
- Have a guild member sponsor them<br>
- Have 6 officers support there application<br>
- Not receive a veto. Any member can veto.<br>
<br>
Getting into the hand is more about forming friendships than applying to uberguild_1 - uberguild_5 on all the various guild web sites.<br>
